1
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,951
When was Brazil discovered ?


2
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,195
In 1500.

3
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,833
Again.

4
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:45,757
Independance, which year ?

5
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:51,280
1822.

6
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:55,750
Freedom for slaves ?

7
00:01:58,240 --> 00:02:01,596
In 1888.

8
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,637
The Republic ? Which year ?

9
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:12,037
1889.

10
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,908
The year of the death of Lampiao ?

11
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:24,478
1938.

12
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:33,719
"I came here,
- I have no family, nor a name -"

13
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:36,100
"pulled by the wind,"

14
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:38,668
"for a last fight against hunger."

15
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:43,035
"I carry with me the people
of this brazilian sertao."


16
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:47,310
"I've put back on my head
a cangaceiro hat."

17
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:51,437
"I want to see the men
of this town appear."

18
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:54,791
"The pride and the wealthy
of the dragon of spite."

19
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:59,869
"Today I'm going away,
but someday, I'll be back."

20
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:03,550
"And, to this pitiless day,
not a stone will survive."

21
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:06,395
"Because vengeance has two faces :"

22
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,273
"the one of Love,
and the one of Hate."


23
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:12,790
"Say three Our Father's.
Lampiao, Our Lord !"

24
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,393
Dr Mattos,

25
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:36,199
I remember
as if it was yesterday.

26
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:39,999
On a road, I met Lampiao.

27
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:44,839
He stopped by, and from his eyes
pure tears flowed.

28
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,916
And he added : "Antonio..."

29
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,955
"Don't you want to join the cangaçao ?"

30
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,752
Doctor...

31
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:59,399
I wanted to, but...
my pride made me refuse.

32
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:03,835
The good-looking and blond 
Corisco then appeared.

33
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:06,156
He said to him :

34
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,669
"Let me bleed this ape."

35
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,755
But Lampiao answered him :

36
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:15,397
"Not him, he's a man of honor."

37
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,830
"He's an enemy, but he's loyal."

38
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:23,313
Dr Mattos,
Lampiao was my mirror.

39
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:29,431
The next morning,
I was already hunting him.

40
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:34,838
One day, in the middle of a road

41
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:37,833
and in the middle of a gunfight,
Lampiao would yell at me :

42
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,474
"Antonio, Is it you Antonio ?"

43
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:45,758
When Corisco did recognize me,
he became mad.

44
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:48,713
He jumped and shot...

45
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:53,039
and the wind shook his hair...


46
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,993
which floated like gold flags.

47
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,630
Then, I killed him

48
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:16,231
and everything was over.

49
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:22,991
And now you tell me,

50
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:28,193
that there's still cangaceiros...

51
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,711
I can't believe you.

52
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:39,074
I agree to do what you ask me to.

53
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,430
But I don't want money.

54
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:48,989
I'll go to the Garden of the Piranhas,
to see if it's true...

55
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,794
that they still exist.

56
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,154
Madalena,

57
00:08:57,800 --> 00:09:00,109
ready my old trunk,

58
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:04,152
put in my rifle and my hat.

59
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,916
I'm traveling.

60
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:17,312
Cursed by ten churches

61
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:27,790
Rejected by all saints

62
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:36,030
Antonio das Mortes

63
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:44,672
Killer of the Cangaceiros

64
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,519
Bring him on, Batista.

65
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:42,198
Bring him on!

66
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,158
It's him, Laura.

67
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:54,434
Coronel, here's Antonio das Mortes.

68
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:59,798
He came to watch over the cangaceiros...

69
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:03,032
I asked you for police reinforcements.

70
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,832
Antonio is better.

71
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:08,430
If he kills, there will be no investigation,

72
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:11,916
nor questioning,
nor press article.

73
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:15,110
And he doesn't want money.

74
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:20,030
Mattos, a free mercenary
brings bad luck.

75
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:22,555
Furthermore, it's useless.

76
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:25,718
Some say that this cangaceiro
is nothing but theater.

77
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,758
Maybe, coronel,

78
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:32,394
but a "nothing" could spoil the future
of the Garden of the Piranhas.

79
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,116
I want to install industry.

80
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:39,434
Investors from the south
will require order.

81
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:43,078
We must end the violence.

82
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:45,949
The agrarian reform will resolve the struggles.

83
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:49,232
What ? Agrarian reform ?

84
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:52,188
Yes, coronel,
Agrarian reform.

85
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:54,231
This is the progress,
sign of the times.

86
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:57,079
Me, to share my lands ?

87
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,512
Did you become crazy ?

88
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:03,074
To share my lands,
with these work-shies ?

89
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:05,350
Is the government mad ?

90
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:08,632
It is not its task to care about
the things of the land.


91
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,353
It's mine.

92
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:13,837
It has to care about machines.
The land, it's my business.

93
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,877
Don't talk to me about american help,

94
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:19,470
agrarian reform or industry 
and other lies.

95
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:23,113
I only know my cows.

96
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:26,432
Something else.
I don't fear no misfortune.

97
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:30,078
And I don't need Antonio das Mortes.

98
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:32,392
I only want Laura.

99
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:38,436
Laura, my love, come near me.

100
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:43,311
Agrarian reform... To share
my lands with these work-shies...

101
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:45,511
They'll have to fight too.

102
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,950
I don't share my sweat.

103
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:53,037
They'll have to kill me
to take over my lands.


104
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:55,955
The elder is becoming mad.

105
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:59,472
Go set your stuff down,
and wait for my orders.

106
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:07,675
Laura, you'll always be by my side.

107
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:12,754
To share my lands with these work-shies ?!

108
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,439
Batista,

109
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:17,230
If Dr Getulio Varg still lived,

110
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:20,314
nobody would dare to 
take over our lands.

111
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:24,275
The guilty about all of that...
Atomic bomb...

112
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:04,271
There's beautifull women in town.

113
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,549
You should meet them.

114
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:09,275
To do what ?
You already have one in the neighborhood.

115
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,189
It's not me who says that.

116
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:16,994
The people are talking, commissar.


117
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:19,714
Vox populi, vox dei.

118
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,753
Did you learn latin from the priest ?

119
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:25,236
By the way, the priest
wants me to become the prefect.

120
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:28,671
What a frightening challenger for me !

121
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:30,199
What's your political platform ?

122
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,753
The pulpit !

123
00:14:37,280 --> 00:14:39,111
Will you become a sexton ?

124
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:42,949
I don't have any access to the bed,
or the dinner table of a coronel.

125
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:48,953
I'm going to be prefect, then deputy.

126
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,553
And then, senator.

127
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:53,638
I'll find you a good job, with
a regular salary.

128
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:56,957
Good. I wasn't paid for
the last six months.

129
00:14:57,160 --> 00:14:58,479
No pessimism.

130
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:00,875
A great economic cycle begins.

131
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:03,594
I only know the cycle of cocoa.

132
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:07,031
The cycle of coffee, of gold,
the one of diamond...

133
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:11,756
The cycle of sugar, of petrol 
and of the rubber.

134
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:17,749
The dollar is the savior 
of this country.


135
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:21,817
Will it save the country,
or its receiver ?

136
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:30,798
I loved, I loved too much.

137
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,714
I suffered from love

138
00:15:33,920 --> 00:15:35,399
like nobody else

139
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:39,270
I've cried, and I've lost peace

140
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:41,954
I know that nobody never ever...

141
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:44,799
The 'cachaça', you pay it !

142
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:29,793
My Saint...

143
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:34,879
The time has come. The time to burn 
the living ones and to destroy the town.

144
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:39,032
I have to fulfill my vow.

145
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:43,710
For the angels' happiness, and
the people's happiness.

146
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:46,998
Show respect to God, Captain Coirana.

147
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,954
Respect god and the government.

148
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:51,991
To respect ?

149
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:55,712
And who shows respect to us ?

150
00:16:57,640 --> 00:17:00,552
Us, poor wandering unhappy ones ?

151
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:06,153
Only vengeance shall permit us to
forget the years of suffering.


152
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:12,072
Without respect.
Absolutly no respect.

153
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:17,308
It has been proved in the past,
and it will be proved in the future :

154
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:20,316
the one who fights against the government

155
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:22,272
shall pay with his own head.

156
00:17:24,280 --> 00:17:26,635
The unhappy cries.

157
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:34,678
The destiny of poverty is hell.

158
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:42,630
I want to embark again on my whithe ship...

159
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:45,355
and sail back to Africa.

160
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:49,192
My Grandfather's Africa.

161
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:54,594
Negro Antao,
you are bathing in fear.

162
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:57,829
You are at the limits of ignorance.

163
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:02,480
Future lies beyond future.

164
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:05,035
Not before past.

165
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:09,834
I've traveled around the world

166
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:14,032
I've seen the misfortunes of other peoples.

167
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:21,636
I've learned this Truth from The Holy Book :

168
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:25,435
"An eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth."

169
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:32,040
In 1945,

170
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:37,355
When Brazil entered the war 
in the Far Europe,

171
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:41,159
it was the dictature of Vargas.

172
00:18:42,800 --> 00:18:45,189
Did Brazil win this war ?

173
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:46,839
Didn't it ?

174
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:50,717
For myself, I've lost them all.

175
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:55,429
By fear and cowardise.

176
00:18:58,040 --> 00:19:00,713
I've even lost the sight of my enemy.

177
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:03,312
Professor...

178
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:07,470
Do you see this hand ?

179
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:11,474
This hand killed many cangaceiros...

180
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:16,993
And now, I'm alone...
In the loneliness of memories.

181
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:21,470
I have to find another enemy.

182
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:25,234
To give a meaning to my life.

183
00:19:26,360 --> 00:19:28,954
I want to see,

184
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:33,754
if Coirana really is a cangaceiro.

185
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:37,315
If he exists, professor,

186
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:40,278
I have to kill him.

187
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:44,710
My heart

188
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,353
What is the reason for

189
00:20:46,560 --> 00:20:47,879
You to beat so quickly

190
00:20:48,120 --> 00:20:49,519
When he sees you

191
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:52,393
And my eyes start to laugh

192
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:55,717
They hunt you, on the street

193
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,751
However

194
00:20:57,960 --> 00:20:59,188
You run away

195
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:02,597
If only you'd know how sweet I am

196
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:04,950
And how much I want you

197
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:09,358
If you knew how much I'm sincere,
you would stay by my side

198
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:10,754
Come

199
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:15,955
Come feel the warm

200
00:21:16,320 --> 00:21:18,788
Of my lips

201
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,479
They're seeking yours

202
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:23,911
Come to quench this passion

203
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:26,515
which is devouring my heart

204
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:29,075
Then only

205
00:21:29,280 --> 00:21:30,679
I'll know happiness

206
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,836
The great happiness

207
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:35,520
"They are more than thousands in debt to me.

208
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:38,871
"But if I enumerate them all,
The earth will shake.

209
00:24:39,560 --> 00:24:43,030
"I'm claiming for the debts in the
Lampiao's testament.

210
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:46,597
"A man has to become a woman,
A woman has to ask for mercy.

211
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:50,835
"Freedom for the prisoner,
prison for the jailer.

212
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:55,639
"A white veil for the whore
who will marry at the Church.

213
00:24:56,280 --> 00:25:00,068
"Money for my poverty, and
something to eat for my people


214
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:02,914
"Honor my revendications,
or I'll come back."

215
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:05,315
Are you of flesh ? Are you of shadows ?

216
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,877
Anwer that, cursed cangaceiro !

217
00:25:08,080 --> 00:25:11,709
I don't believe in your
ridiculous clothing.

218
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:15,629
"First, tell me your name,
then wear off your disguise."

219
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:19,477
"Who talk like this is
already condemned."

220
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:21,591
Open your ears.

221
00:25:22,120 --> 00:25:24,031
I am Antonio das Mortes.

222
00:25:24,600 --> 00:25:28,673
Here to frighten your cowardise,
and to override your destiny.

223
00:25:29,440 --> 00:25:33,479
And I add,
not on brazilian territory,

224
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:35,877
nor in heaven, nor in hell :

225
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:38,191
there is no place for
a new cangaceiro !

226
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:41,716
Be ready, my people !
And look at the duel

227
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:44,593
between the dragon of cruelty
and the holy warrior.

228
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:49,191
From Corisco to Lampiao,
no more soul-in-sorrow in hell.

229
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:50,435
Be ready !

230
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:53,598
I'm going to end up with your race,
Antonio das Mortes.

231
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:57,996
Come, I'm waiting,
Antonio das Mortes !

232
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:50,236
The Piranhas took me !

233
00:28:55,360 --> 00:28:57,794
The Piranhas are devouring me !

234
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:05,069
Mattos, put an end to these chants !

235
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:07,630
Put an end to these chants !

236
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:14,838
I am coronel Horacio,
I order you to stop singing !

237
00:29:15,360 --> 00:29:18,318
Batista, make them stop !

238
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:24,069
Put an end to that devil chant !

239
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:28,319
They have to stop,
I'm ordering it !

240
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:31,034
Laura, put an end to these chants !

241
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:38,353
They have to stop,
It's an order !

242
00:29:39,080 --> 00:29:41,150
Coronel Horacio is ordering

243
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,915
these chants to be ceased !

244
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:25,317
I'm like a father to you,

245
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:28,595
The Garden of the Piranhas is poor,

246
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:31,912
Look at me,
my clothes, my home...

247
00:30:33,160 --> 00:30:36,709
The government is making fun of me,
by promising food,

248
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:38,956
money for the poors,

249
00:30:39,360 --> 00:30:42,591
drugs, a doctor...
But nothing comes.

250
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:44,918
My hands are tied,

251
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:48,158
I can't nourish all of you. 
I'm not the Christ.

252
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:49,998
I'm a good man,

253
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:52,750
But I can't do miracles.

254
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:55,831
Did you hear me ?

255
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:59,998
Go away, all of you !

256
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:03,078
Wait, I'll do you charity.

257
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:06,399
Batista, open the store

258
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:08,750
and give them some flour and meat.

259
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:11,679
Remember, it's charity.

260
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:16,877
Mattos, that's a charitable act,

261
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:19,431
I'm going to nourish every one,

