and a rifle at hand

529
01:03:13,080 --> 01:03:14,433
My Saint...

530
01:03:16,200 --> 01:03:18,714
This cangaceiro is mine.

531
01:03:21,120 --> 01:03:24,317
Let me bury him 
at the heart of this sertao.

532
01:03:57,920 --> 01:03:59,114
Mata Vaca...

533
01:04:00,600 --> 01:04:02,716
End that act of Justice.

534
01:04:05,360 --> 01:04:07,999
You must put an end to the pestiferous.

535
01:06:14,240 --> 01:06:15,434
Professor !

536
01:06:15,640 --> 01:06:19,076
the coronel did order to kill
the saint and her retinue.

537
01:06:19,680 --> 01:06:22,797
And Antonio das Mortes disappeared.

538
01:06:23,680 --> 01:06:25,671
We have to make something !

539
01:06:25,920 --> 01:06:28,388
He ordered to kill them.

540
01:06:28,600 --> 01:06:31,751
The coronel ordered to kill them.

541
01:06:34,040 --> 01:06:37,077
We have to do something !

542
01:06:37,400 --> 01:06:40,870
I can't do anything just by myself.
This one's already dead !

543
01:06:41,600 --> 01:06:44,956
We must care about the living ones!

544
01:06:45,160 --> 01:06:46,991
Care about the living !

545
01:12:27,520 --> 01:12:30,830
Laura, protect me
from the devil of obscurity !

546
01:12:31,200 --> 01:12:32,519
Come, Laura.

547
01:12:34,240 --> 01:12:37,038
I dreamed that Antonio das Mortes
was killing me.

548
01:12:37,240 --> 01:12:40,516
Come near me, Laura.
Protect me.

549
01:12:41,040 --> 01:12:42,439
Mata Vaca must come !

550
01:12:42,920 --> 01:12:44,638
Antonio das Mortes is going to kill me.

551
01:13:39,880 --> 01:13:41,677
It's destiny, my Saint,

552
01:13:43,400 --> 01:13:45,630
that did retain my hand.

553
01:13:48,160 --> 01:13:49,912
I've lost my strength.

554
01:13:50,680 --> 01:13:52,477
I'm not good at anything, anymore.

555
01:13:52,720 --> 01:13:55,917
I'll leave !
Get back to the city !

556
01:13:56,160 --> 01:13:58,993
And it's the same misfortune
I'll find there !

557
01:14:00,960 --> 01:14:05,397
We'll keep bearing the suffering.

558
01:14:10,920 --> 01:14:12,512
Brazil !

559
01:15:38,040 --> 01:15:39,553
And one day an endless war...

560
01:15:41,800 --> 01:15:43,358
will start.

561
01:15:52,880 --> 01:15:56,555
Rise from the dust, rise !

562
01:16:02,000 --> 01:16:05,879
Rise from the dust, rise !

563
01:16:06,680 --> 01:16:12,118
I cried, without hiding.

564
01:16:12,440 --> 01:16:15,591
Everyone saw me.

565
01:16:16,640 --> 01:16:22,670
I wasn't the only one to cry.

566
01:16:22,880 --> 01:16:26,395
But rising like I did,

567
01:16:26,600 --> 01:16:28,909
who could have done the same ?

568
01:16:29,480 --> 01:16:31,710
A strong man

569
01:16:31,920 --> 01:16:33,797
does not stay lying,

570
01:16:34,000 --> 01:16:36,673
refusing that a woman

571
01:16:36,920 --> 01:16:37,830
could give her hand to him

572
01:16:38,040 --> 01:16:42,352
He recognizes his defeat
and don't lose courage.

573
01:16:43,040 --> 01:16:46,749
Rise from the dust, rise !

574
01:16:47,680 --> 01:16:51,275
Rise from the dust, rise !

575
01:18:15,160 --> 01:18:19,438
Hundred of old negros died,
they were not working anymore

576
01:18:21,120 --> 01:18:25,398
A bastard named Traz-Ca,
turned and fell behind

577
01:18:26,120 --> 01:18:29,795
dirty-muzzle and Mustache
- his war name -

578
01:18:30,000 --> 01:18:32,639
Satan's brother-in-law

579
01:18:35,760 --> 01:18:39,958
Here came Lampiao
at the gates of hell

580
01:18:41,640 --> 01:18:45,997
A boy, still young,
appeared at the gate

581
01:18:46,520 --> 01:18:49,114
Who are you horseman ?

582
01:18:49,320 --> 01:18:53,711
I'm a cangaceiro,
answered Lampiao

583
01:18:55,360 --> 01:18:59,876
I'm not your guardian, and
not your comrade

584
01:19:01,320 --> 01:19:05,552
You won't enter here,
except if you tell your name

585
01:19:07,360 --> 01:19:10,989
Boy, open the door,
I am Lampiao

586
01:19:11,200 --> 01:19:13,589
Terror for the entire world

587
01:19:18,920 --> 01:19:23,232
This guardian, responsible for the gate

588
01:19:23,800 --> 01:19:28,112
seeing him like this,
didn't ask questions any more

589
01:19:28,600 --> 01:19:32,354
The Negro knows to write,
but can't read

590
01:19:32,560 --> 01:19:34,869
Here, forgiveness has no place

591
01:19:36,480 --> 01:19:40,917
Then the guardian came and said :
wait for me outside

592
01:19:41,400 --> 01:19:45,518
I'm going to talk with the chief
at the central bureau

593
01:19:46,160 --> 01:19:48,071
If he refuses you

594
01:19:48,280 --> 01:19:52,353
depending on what he'll say,
I'll accept you, or not

595
01:19:54,920 --> 01:19:59,471
Lampiao said : make your mind,
who talks lose time

596
01:20:00,920 --> 01:20:04,310
Go and come back, quick,
I won't wait for long

597
01:20:05,880 --> 01:20:09,475
If they let me enter,
I'll ransack enverything

598
01:20:09,680 --> 01:20:11,875
I'll burn the place and then i'll go away

599
01:21:09,160 --> 01:21:12,914
the guardian found Satan
at the saloon

600
01:21:13,480 --> 01:21:17,837
Know my Lord that Lampiao is at the door

601
01:21:18,360 --> 01:21:22,035
And pretend to be willing to enter

602
01:21:22,360 --> 01:21:24,794
Should I let him do so ?

603
01:21:27,440 --> 01:21:31,513
No, answered Satan,
Tell him to go away

604
01:21:32,080 --> 01:21:36,312
There's only riffraff coming in,
I'm furious

605
01:21:36,880 --> 01:21:43,069
I'd like to
 drive out half of the ones
that are already in.

606
01:21:46,720 --> 01:21:50,759
Lampiao is a bandit,
a thief of honesty

607
01:21:51,560 --> 01:21:55,439
he wants to spread confusion

608
01:21:56,400 --> 01:22:00,109
why would we encumber ourselves 
with such a man

609
01:22:00,320 --> 01:22:02,675
without absolute necessity ?

610
01:22:04,120 --> 01:22:08,318
The guardian said :
Lord, what a disaster !

611
01:22:08,920 --> 01:22:13,516
There will be uprising,
if we don't let him enter

612
01:22:15,840 --> 01:22:19,469
Don't worry, said Satan,
call the negros

613
01:22:19,680 --> 01:22:22,319
Take as many as you need

614
01:22:23,600 --> 01:22:27,832
Hundreds should come, men and women

615
01:22:28,480 --> 01:22:32,758
go to the warehouse, and take all
the weapons you need

616
01:22:33,240 --> 01:22:39,554
Other fellows of Lucifer
should be advised too

617
01:22:41,000 --> 01:22:42,911
The negros came

618
01:22:43,120 --> 01:22:45,350
first, came Fuchico

619
01:22:46,120 --> 01:22:50,193
armed with an old rifle
and shouting to Pea-brain

620
01:22:50,680 --> 01:22:56,596
to bring his whip
and to call Tangença by Maçarico

621
01:22:58,320 --> 01:23:02,711
Then came Cambota,
checking his weapons

622
01:23:03,280 --> 01:23:07,273
Formigueiro, Trupe-Zupe
and Quele came

623
01:23:08,080 --> 01:23:11,675
then Banzeiro, Pacaia,
Rabisca, Cordao de Saia

624
01:23:11,880 --> 01:23:14,155
and finally, Baze

625
01:23:18,840 --> 01:23:23,118
Then came a young she-devil
dressed with fine lingerie

626
01:23:24,640 --> 01:23:28,599
She pushed the fence, and said
that it was some bad times

627
01:23:29,480 --> 01:23:31,311
And that today would be a hard day

628
01:23:31,520 --> 01:23:35,593
She shouted at the Baiana,
that now, it was serious

629
01:23:37,080 --> 01:23:41,278
Then this armed band 
went to the camp

630
01:23:41,880 --> 01:23:46,112
With rifles, sabers and daggers

631
01:23:46,760 --> 01:23:50,355
There was negress with her cook knife

632
01:23:50,560 --> 01:23:52,915
and her manioc rammer

633
01:23:56,280 --> 01:24:00,512
When Lampiao saw
this band of armed negros

634
01:24:01,200 --> 01:24:02,952
He said : 
It's only in Abyssinia

635
01:24:03,160 --> 01:24:05,355
where we should find such an army

636
01:24:05,880 --> 01:24:09,634
Arms at hands,
the chief of this army shouted :

637
01:24:09,840 --> 01:24:12,400
Everyone on him, my negros !

638
01:24:13,640 --> 01:24:15,312
Antonio das Mortes !

639
01:24:19,520 --> 01:24:23,069
Mata Vaca and a handfull of mercenaries are here,

640
01:24:23,680 --> 01:24:26,797
ready to pour their own blood

641
01:24:27,480 --> 01:24:29,869
to defend their protector.

642
01:24:31,560 --> 01:24:34,916
Listen to me.
I fought against Lampaio,

643
01:24:35,200 --> 01:24:36,792
and against Antonio Conselheiro,

644
01:24:37,120 --> 01:24:39,270
But I'm one of them.


645
01:24:41,000 --> 01:24:42,558
Antonio das Mortes !

646
01:24:43,400 --> 01:24:46,039
Show that you're a man.

647
01:24:46,680 --> 01:24:51,708
Let's fight at the front of this church.

648
01:24:52,240 --> 01:24:55,312
with this coward crowd,
hiding behind windows

649
01:24:55,520 --> 01:24:58,159
and under the beds, 
for witness

650
01:24:59,880 --> 01:25:01,632
Antonio das Mortes !

651
01:25:07,400 --> 01:25:09,550
If God helps a criminal

652
01:25:10,480 --> 01:25:12,357
Then he'll help me :

653
01:25:13,200 --> 01:25:16,192
I've shed less blood than you.

654
01:25:16,640 --> 01:25:18,756
Show that you're a man !

655
01:25:19,120 --> 01:25:20,872
Coronel!

656
01:25:24,600 --> 01:25:26,636
The time has come.

657
01:25:27,320 --> 01:25:30,437
The town will open its eyes.

658
01:25:31,440 --> 01:25:36,195
The one who talks
never shed any blood,

659
01:25:36,680 --> 01:25:40,593
But he's ready to shed his own

660
01:25:41,200 --> 01:25:45,239
to avenge the humiliated sertao.

661
01:25:45,840 --> 01:25:48,912
And I'd say like the holy Book :

662
01:25:49,640 --> 01:25:53,918
" An eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth. "

663
01:25:54,320 --> 01:25:56,311
You truly are the angel of the Pest,

664
01:25:57,240 --> 01:25:59,515
The mad beast I was waiting for.

665
01:26:00,400 --> 01:26:02,914
It could not have been Coirana.

666
01:26:05,160 --> 01:26:07,628
It could only be someone like you,

667
01:26:07,840 --> 01:26:10,991
One of these wanderers,
who came from the cities

668
01:26:11,280 --> 01:26:13,794
to sow the ideas of destruction.

669
01:26:14,000 --> 01:26:17,595
Talk, goon, I'm listening to you.

670
01:26:18,800 --> 01:26:19,915
Professor,

671
01:26:21,200 --> 01:26:23,714
I wanted to say...

672
01:26:26,240 --> 01:26:28,595
We are fighting together,

673
01:26:29,360 --> 01:26:31,476
but not with the same weapons.

674
01:26:33,000 --> 01:26:35,309
yours are political,

675
01:26:37,000 --> 01:26:39,116
mine have to do with God.

676
01:26:39,800 --> 01:26:41,119
Okay, Antonio.

677
01:26:43,600 --> 01:26:45,636
We share the enemy.

678
01:26:47,200 --> 01:26:50,078
You keep all your bravery.


679
01:26:50,320 --> 01:26:52,436
I'll stay in your shadow.

680
01:26:54,080 --> 01:26:55,672
No, professor.

681
01:26:57,040 --> 01:26:59,634
Fight with your ideals,

682
01:27:00,560 --> 01:27:02,790
they matter much more than me.

683
01:27:05,760 --> 01:27:08,228
I want to see the famous Mata Vaca !

684
01:27:08,640 --> 01:27:11,234
Coward, son of an ape !

685
01:27:13,280 --> 01:27:15,874
God, let me end my task.

686
01:27:16,560 --> 01:27:19,472
I'm readying myself to show up before You.

687
01:29:35,720 --> 01:29:40,111
The battle was now lasting since
more than one hour

688
01:29:40,640 --> 01:29:44,758
Dust was flying everywhere
and the negros were crying

689
01:29:45,400 --> 01:29:50,997
Lampiao, even if wounded,
would not give away

690
01:29:55,800 --> 01:30:00,157
Lampiao threw a rock at a dog

691
01:30:00,560 --> 01:30:04,712
But the rock blew up
the window of the store

692
01:30:05,400 --> 01:30:10,952
A fire started to grow
in the cotton reserve

693
01:30:13,880 --> 01:30:18,192
Satan, looking at the fire,
called his men back

694
01:30:19,600 --> 01:30:24,116
All the negros came to him

695
01:30:24,360 --> 01:30:30,037
Lampiao went away, having no more enemies

696
01:30:35,000 --> 01:30:39,278
This day was a great loss for Satan

697
01:30:39,760 --> 01:30:43,958
All his wealth burned to dust

698
01:30:44,520 --> 01:30:50,470
his record book burned,
and all his goods

699
01:30:52,120 --> 01:30:56,352
Lucifer said :
No more horrors,

700
01:30:56,880 --> 01:31:00,998
why such a misfortune ?

701
01:31:01,600 --> 01:31:06,993
I'll have the longest winter of my life !

702
01:31:09,960 --> 01:31:14,556
And now I'm going to end up 
that story with Lampaio

703
01:31:14,880 --> 01:31:18,998
This is not my business,
but I give you my point of view

704
01:31:19,640 --> 01:31:24,760
He is not in heaven, nor in hell,
but still is in the sertao !

705
01:31:27,120 --> 01:31:31,113
If you don't believe my story

706
01:31:31,760 --> 01:31:35,639
If you do not trust my honesty

707
01:31:36,480 --> 01:31:39,836
You can write in hell and ask to Satan

708
01:31:40,040 --> 01:31:42,793
If this story is true, or not

709
01:32:13,560 --> 01:32:18,236
Cursed by ten chruches

710
01:32:23,200 --> 01:32:29,116
Rejected by all saints

711
01:32:32,760 --> 01:32:37,754
Antonio das Mortes

712
01:32:40,880 --> 01:32:46,193
Killer of cangaceiros...